        "@value": "Attempted child sex trafficking undercover sting: CI-facilitated commercial sex negotiation for minor under 14, proof-of-life images, travel with $500 cash — disrupted at meet before hands-on act. Sources: indictment (Doc 1), plea agreement (Doc 18), sentencing memorandum (Doc 23). Evidentiary basis: PROVEN."
